title: American Horror Story Season 8 BREAKING NEWS
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: I hope the subtitle for the Murder House/Coven crossover is AHS: Occult, since both seasons revolve around Ghosts and Witches; the Supernatural. I think the cast will being playing new characters and the season will have its own story that will connect to Murder House and Coven.
I’m not surprised that cross over wasn’t season 9. It didn’t make sense. I hope AHS doesn’t stop at 9. I still hope it will become like Dr. Who and just goes on indefinitely.
AHHHHHHH OHMYGODDDDDDDD NO WAY, I've been SO pumped for this since I heard about it, my two favorite seasons smashed together and we get it a year early :')
I’m sooo frickin’ excited!!!! Can’t even imagine what will happen!!
